quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif Lam Ra. Tsino ni tsinyali tsieshitabu nende Ikurani yinoosinjia
  15,2,Awundi balitsa bekomba balia bakhaya mbu bamanyanga baba Abasalamu
  15,3,"Baleshesa balie ebiakhulia mana basangale, mana bakatibwe nende liparo lwobubeyi (mbu balileshelwa), ahambi ano betsa okhumanya"
  15,4,Ne shikhwasishiakhwo olukongo lwosi lwosi tawe halali lwali nende ebise bialwo bimanyikhane
  15,5,"Ne babulaho Abandu bosi bosi banyala okhwuranjilila ebise bieyindukho biabu, nohomba shibanyala okhushindibwa tawe"
  15,6,"Nebaboola mbu; “ Ewe ulia oweshilibwakhwo amestulisio, toto ewe oli omulalu”"
  15,7,“Shichila shina nolakhurerera Abamalaika nikali mbu ewe oli mubaboolanga obwatoto?’’
  15,8,"Efwe shikhwishinjia Abamalaika halali khubwatoto (ebise biokhusishibwa khwabu nibiula), ne awo shibalihebwa obwiyangu tawe (balisishibwa butswa)"
  15,9,"Toto efwe khweshia ametsulisio kano, ne khandi toto efwe nefwe khwitsa okhukalinda"
  15,10,Ne toto khwaruma Abarumwa mumikanda chia Abandu beyimbeli
  15,11,Ne Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselanga halali bo bamukholelanga omubayo
  15,12,Ne endio nilwakhwinjisinjia mumioyo chia balia abamabii
  15,13,"Shibasuubilanga kano tawe, ne bamala okhulola shingala kali khubandu bali imbeli wabu eyo"
  15,14,Ne khubafungulilanga omuliango kwo mwikulu mana baba nibaninanga
  15,15,Kho bakhaboolele mbu; “tsimoni tsiefu tsimeesibwe ne efwe abeene khulochelwe.”
  15,16,"Ne toto khwara mwikulu tsing’ining’ini, mana nikhutsirona khubalia bokhuhenga"
  15,17,Ne khwatsilinda okhurulana nende buli Shetani ulondungwa
  15,18,"Halali ulia uwulilisinjia mukhwiba, naye mana, amulondangakhwo nende eshichenga shiomulilo shilolokha"
  15,19,Ne liloba khwaliala mana nikhuramwo tsingulu ne nikhumesiamwo buli eshindu khushichelo
  15,20,"Ne nikhubakasiliamwo obulamu, nende ebindi bia enywe mulabikabilanga tawe"
  15,21,"Ne shibulaho shiosi shiosi halali shirula khwifwe, nesikhushiishinjia tawe halali khushichelo shimanyishe"
  15,22,"Ne khureranga omuyeka kwitsulemwo liime, ne khwishinjia amatsi okhurula mumaleesi ako. Mana khubanywesinjia amatsi ako. Ne shimuli enywe mukabikhanga tawe"
  15,23,"Ne ni efwe khulamusinjia ne ninefwe abafwisinjia, na ni efwe nefwe abalichelama. (abalikalusia)"
  15,24,"Ne khwamanya abaranjililanga mwinywe, nekhumanyile abatong’a inyuma"
  15,25,Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo niye wakhabakhung’asie toto Ye niye Owamachesi Omumanyi muno
  15,26,"Ne toto khwalonga Omundu okhurula khwiloba eliumu, elirusinjia- omwoyo- isauti(nilituywa) elirulana nende amatoyi karebwakhwo ifwani"
  15,27,"Ne Amajiini khwakalonga imbeli awo, okhurulana nende omuyeka kwo mulilo"
  15,28,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo olwayaboolela Malaika mbu; “Toto esie nditsa okhulonga Omundu okhurula khuliloba liwumukhanga, lirulana nende amatoyi akarebwamwo ifwani"
  15,29,"Kho olwa ndalamala okhumulonga mana nemufuramwo emiuya chianje, mumwinamile khulwa okhumuwa eshiribwa"
  15,30,Abamalaika boosi halala nibamwinamila
  15,31,"Halali Ibilisi, yakhaya okhuba halala nende balia benama"
  15,32,(Nyasaye)Naboola mbu; “Ewe Ibilisi obele orie olabeele halala nende abenaame?”
  15,33,"Naboola; “Shenyala okhwinamila Omundu wawaloonga khuliloba eliumu lirusinjia -omwoyo- isauti, elirula khu matoyi karebwakhwo ifwani tawe.”"
  15,34,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “ rula omo, oli omutsube’’"
  15,35,Ne toto oli nende eshilamo shianje okhula inyanga yeyindukho.”
  15,36,Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi! Mbelesie obwiyangu okhula inyanga yabalilamusibwa”
  15,37,(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “toto ewe olimubalia bahebwa obwiyangu
  15,38,Okhula inyanga yebise bimanyishe biarebwaho .”
  15,39,Naboola;“Nyasayewanje!shingalawambusilia okhukora nditsa okhubaronela(abandu) khushialo ne nditsa okhubakosia boosi.”
  15,40,Halali Abasumba bobo abatswenufu”
  15,41,(Nyasaye) naboola mbu “ino ni injila yokhwitsa ewanje ingololofu”
  15,42,"“Ne toto Abandu banje ewe sholaba nende obunyali khubo tawe, halali balia abakori bakhulondakhwo"
  15,43,"Ne toto Jahannam niho habundu wabu, wabakasilibwa bosi"
  15,44,"Ili nende emiliango saba, nebuli omuliango kuli nende ebuleka yakabulwa"
  15,45,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda nende tsisebele
  15,46,“Injilemwo mushironyo nomulembe”
  15,47,"Ne khulirusia amakhonye akali mubilifu biabu, ne baliba (shinga) Abananda nibekhale khubisala biobwami nibahengana"
  15,48,"Shibulibatilakhwo obuchong’e bwosi bwosi omo tawe, ne shibalirusibwamwo tawe"
  15,49,Boolela Abasumba banje mbu esie nesie Owobulesheli obunji Owetsimbabaasi muno